#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&klipper; is the &plasma; clipboard utility. It stores clipboard history, "
"and allows you to link clipboard contents to application actions. Please "
"report any problems or feature requests to <ulink url=\"http://bugs.kde.org"
"\">KDEs bugzilla</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&klipper; je &plasma; pripomoček za odložišče. Shranjuje zgodovino odložišča "
"in omogoča povezovanje vsebine odložišča z dejanji aplikacije. "
"Prosimsporočite vse težave ali zahteve po funkcijah na <ulink url=\"http://"
"bugs.kde.org\">KDEs bugzilla</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &klipper;"
msgstr "Uporaba &klipper;ja"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Basic Usage"
msgstr "Osnovna uporaba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use &klipper; in the systemtray either as &plasma; widget or classic "
"application. Both share the same functionality but have a different &GUI; "
"and show the last item of the history when hovering the &klipper; icon in "
"the systemtray:"
msgstr ""
"Uporabite lahko &klipper; v sistemski vrstici kot &plasma; gradnik ali "
"klasična aplikacija. Oba imata enako funkcionalnost, vendar imata drugačen "
"&GUI; in prikažite zadnji element zgodovine, ko miško &klipper; ikona v "
"sistemski vrstici:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &klipper; icon."
msgstr "Ikona &klipper;ja."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &klipper; icon"
msgstr "Ikona &klipper;ja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &klipper; widget is hidden if the clipboard is empty."
msgstr "&klipper; gradnik je skrit, če je odložišče prazno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To display the clipboard history, click on the &klipper; icon in the "
"systemtray."
msgstr ""
"Za prikaz zgodovine odložišča kliknite &klipper; ikona v sistemski vrstici."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "&klipper; Widget"
msgstr "&klipper; gradnik"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &klipper; Widget."
msgstr "Gradnik &klipper;ja."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &klipper; Widget"
msgstr "Gradnik &klipper;ja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hover an entry with the mouse pointer and four icons appear which enable you "
"to invoke an action, show the barcode, edit the content or remove the entry "
"from the history. Use &spectacle; to capture the barcodes and save them."
msgstr ""
"S kazalcem miške premaknite vnos in prikažejo se štiri ikone, ki vam "
"omogočajo, da prikličete dejanje, prikažete črtno kodo, uredite vsebino ali "
"odstranite vnos iz zgodovine. Uporabite &spectacle; za zajemanje črtnih kod "
"in njihovo shranjevanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can search through the clipboard history by opening it (click on "
"&klipper;) and typing your query. The results are updated as you type. To "
"clear the clipboard history click on the icon at the right of the search "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Po zgodovini odložišča lahko iščete tako, da ga odprete (kliknite &klipper;) "
"in vnesete svojo poizvedbo. Rezultati se posodabljajo med tipkanjem. Če "
"želite počistiti zgodovino odložišča, kliknite ikono na desni strani "
"iskalnega polja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Configure Clipboard...</guilabel> action in the context menu "
"opens the <link linkend=\"preferences\">settings dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Dejanje <guilabel>Konfiguriraj odložišče ...</guilabel> v kontekstnem meniju "
"odpre <link linkend=\"preferences\">pogovorno okno z nastavitvami</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Actions"
msgstr "Dejanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&klipper; can perform actions on the contents of the clipboard, based on "
"whether they match a particular regular expression. For example, any "
"clipboard contents starting with <quote>http://</quote> can be passed to "
"Firefox or &konqueror; as &URL;s to open. In addition, if the contents "
"matches a path, similar actions can be performed according to the file's "
"type. &eg;, if the path to a <acronym>PDF</acronym> file is copied to the "
"clipboard, the file can be viewed in &okular;."
msgstr ""
"&klipper; lahko izvaja dejanja na vsebini odložišča na podlagi ali ujemanja "
"z določenim regularnim izrazom. Na primer, kateri koli vsebino odložišča, ki "
"se začne z <quote>http://</quote>, je mogoče posredovati programu Firefox "
"ali &konqueror; kot &URL; za odpiranje. Poleg tega, če vsebina se ujema s "
"potjo, lahko podobna dejanja izvedete glede na vrsto datoteke. &eg;, če je "
"pot do datoteke <acronym>PDF</acronym> prekopirana na odložišče, si lahko "
"datoteko ogledate v programu &okular;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To use this feature, just select a &URL; or path. If there is a matching "
"regular expression in &klipper;'s list, a menu will appear showing you the "
"programs for your selection. Use the mouse or cursor keys to select a "
"program, and &klipper; will run this program, opening the address pointed to "
"by the selection."
msgstr ""
"Za uporabo te zmožnosti samo izberite &URL; ali pot. Če obstaja "
"ujemanjeregularnega izraza na seznamu &klipper;, se bo prikazal meni, ki vam "
"bo prikazalprogrami po vaši izbiri. Z miško ali smernimi tipkami izberite "
"program in &klipper; bo zagnal ta program in odprl navedeni izbrani naslov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can change the time that the menu remains for in the settings dialog, "
"with the option <guilabel>Show action popup menu</guilabel> under the "
"<guilabel>General</guilabel> page. You can separately disable the file path "
"part using the option <guilabel>Include MIME actions</guilabel> under the "
"<guilabel>Action Menu</guilabel> page."
msgstr ""
"Čas prikaza menija lahko spremenite v pogovornem oknu z nastavitvami z "
"možnostjo <guilabel>Prikaži pojavni meni dejanj</guilabel> na strani "
"<guilabel>Splošno</guilabel>. Del poti datoteke lahko ločeno onemogočite z "
"možnostjo <guilabel>Vključi dejanja MIME</guilabel> na strani <guilabel>Meni "
"dejanj</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Actions can be disabled completely by pressing the shortcut <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Dejanja lahko popolnoma onemogočite s pritiskom na bližnjico <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clipboard contents which match a regular expression can also be edited "
"before performing an action on them. Select <guimenuitem>Edit contents...</"
"guimenuitem> at the right of the clipboard entry, and you can change the "
"clipboard contents in the dialog which appears, before clicking the "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton> button to run the appropriate action."
msgstr ""
"Vsebino odložišča, ki se ujema z regularnim izrazom, je mogoče tudi "
"urejatipreden izvedete dejanje na njih. Izberite <guimenuitem>Uredi "
"vsebino...</guimenuitem> na desni strani vnosa v odložišče in lahko "
"spremenite vsebino odložišča v pogovornem oknu, ki se prikaže, preden "
"kliknete gumb <guibutton>V redu</guibutton> za zagon ustreznega dejanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> "
"shows the pop-up menu to repeat the last action which &klipper; performed."
msgstr ""
"Pritisk na <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>R</keycap></"
"keycombo> prikaže menu za ponovitev zadnjega &klipper;jevega dejanja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clipboard/Selection Behavior"
msgstr "Odložišče/Izbirno vedenje"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid "General"
msgstr "Splošno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&klipper; can be used to set the behavior of the clipboard and selection in "
"&plasma;."
msgstr ""
"&klipper; lahko uporabite za nastavitev obnašanja odložišča in izbire v "
"&plasma;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &X-Window; uses two separate clipboard buffers: the <quote>selection</"
"quote> and the <quote>clipboard</quote>. Text is placed in the selection "
"buffer by simply selecting it, and can be pasted with the middle mouse "
"button. To place text in the clipboard buffer, select it and press "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap> </keycombo> or <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>C</"
"keycap> </keycombo>. Text from the clipboard buffer is pasted using "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap> </keycombo> or by selecting "
"<guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> in a context menu."
msgstr ""
"&X-Window; uporablja dva ločena medpomnilnika odložišča: <quote>izbor</"
"quote> in <quote>odložišče</quote>. Besedilo se umesti v medpomnilnik za "
"izbiro tako, da ga preprosto izberete, prilepite pa ga lahko s srednjim "
"gumbom miške. Če želite besedilo postaviti v odložiščni medpomnilnik, ga "
"izberite in pritisnite <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap> </keycombo> ali "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap> </keycombo>. Besedilo iz medpomnilnika "
"odložišča se prilepi s tipko <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap> </keycombo> "
"ali z izbiro <guimenuitem>Prilepi</guimenuitem> v priročnem meniju."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changing Clipboard/Selection Behavior"
msgstr "Spreminjanje odložišča/Izbirno vedenje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In order to change clipboard/selection behavior, select "
"<guimenuitem>Configure Clipboard...</guimenuitem> from the &klipper; context "
"menu, and in the dialog box that appears, select the <guilabel>General</"
"guilabel> page. Unchecking <guilabel>Selection and Clipboard</guilabel> "
"makes the clipboard and selection function as completely separate buffers as "
"described above. With this option set, the option <guilabel>Ignore</"
"guilabel> will prevent &klipper; from including the contents of the "
"selection in its clipboard history and from performing actions on the "
"contents of the selection. Selecting <guilabel>Selection and Clipboard</"
"guilabel> causes the clipboard and selection buffers to always be the same, "
"meaning that text in the selection can be pasted with either the "
"<mousebutton>middle</mousebutton> mouse button or the key combination "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap> </keycombo>, and similarly for text in "
"the clipboard buffer."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti odložišče/izbirno vedenje, izberite "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj odložišče...</guimenuitem> iz &klipper; "
"kontekstnega menija in v pogovornem oknu, ki se prikaže, izberite stran "
"<guilabel>Splošno</guilabel>. Če počistite polje <guilabel>Izbira in "
"odložišče</guilabel>, bosta odložišče in izbira delovala kot popolnoma "
"ločena medpomnilnika, kot je opisano zgoraj. Če je nastavljena ta možnost, "
"bo možnost <guilabel>Prezri</guilabel> preprečila &klipper; od vključitve "
"vsebine izbora v zgodovino odložišča in od izvajanja dejanj nad vsebino "
"izbora. Izbira <guilabel>Izbor in odložišče</guilabel> povzroči, da sta "
"odložišče in medpomnilniki izbir vedno enaka, kar pomeni, da lahko besedilo "
"v izboru prilepite z <mousebutton>srednjim</mousebutton> gumbom miške ali s "
"kombinacijo tipk <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap> </keycombo> in podobno "
"za besedilo v medpomnilniku odložišča."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &klipper;"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje &klipper;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Options"
msgstr "Splošne možnosti"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selection and Clipboard"
msgstr "Izbor in odložišče"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When text or an area of the screen is highlighted with the mouse or "
"keyboard, this is the <emphasis>selection</emphasis>. It can be pasted using "
"the middle mouse button."
msgstr ""
"Ko je besedilo ali območje zaslona označeno z miško ali tipkovnico, je to "
"<emphasis>izbor</emphasis>. Prilepite ga lahko s srednjim gumbom miške."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the selection is explicitly copied using a <guimenuitem>Copy</"
"guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem> action, it is saved to the "
"<emphasis>clipboard</emphasis>. It can be pasted using a <guimenuitem>Paste</"
"guimenuitem> action."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbor eksplicitno kopiran z dejanjem <guimenuitem>Kopiraj</"
"guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>Izreži</guimenuitem>, se shrani v "
"<emphasis>odložišče</emphasis>. Prilepite ga lahko z dejanjem "
"<guimenuitem>Prilepi</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When turned on this option keeps the selection and the clipboard the same, "
"so that any selection is immediately available to paste by any means. If it "
"is turned off, the selection may still be saved in the clipboard history "
"(subject to the options below), but it can only be pasted using the middle "
"mouse button."
msgstr ""
"Ko je ta možnost vklopljena, ostaneta izbor in odložišče enaka, tako da je "
"vsak izbor takoj na voljo za lepljenje na kakršen koli način. Če je "
"izklopljen, se lahko izbor še vedno shrani v zgodovino odložišča (v skladu s "
"spodnjimi možnostmi), vendar ga je mogoče prilepiti samo s srednjim gumbom "
"miške."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clipboard history"
msgstr "Zgodovina odložišča"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggles clipboard history."
msgstr "Preklopi zgodovino odložišča."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of entries"
msgstr "Število vnosov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sets the number of items that are stored in the clipboard history."
msgstr "Nastavi število elementov, ki so shranjeni v zgodovini odložišča."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text selection"
msgstr "Izbira besedila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When an area of the screen is selected with mouse or keyboard, this is "
"called the <quote>selection</quote>. This option determines whether text "
"selections are saved in the clipboard history. It is possible to choose "
"between <guilabel>Always save in history</guilabel> and <guilabel>Only when "
"explicitly copied</guilabel>. The <guilabel>Always save in history</"
"guilabel> option is not available if selection/clipboard synchronisation is "
"turned off &dash; in this case the selection is never automatically saved in "
"the clipboard history. See <xref linkend=\"clipboard-modes\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Ko je območje zaslona izbrano z miško ali tipkovnico, se to imenuje "
"<quote>izbor</quote>. Ta možnost določa, ali se izbor besedila shrani v "
"zgodovino odložišča. Izbirate lahko med <guilabel>Vedno shrani v zgodovino</"
"guilabel> in <guilabel>Samo pri eksplicitnem kopiranju</guilabel>. Možnost "
"<guilabel>Vedno shrani v zgodovino</guilabel> ni na voljo, če je "
"sinhronizacija izbira/odložišče izklopljena &dash; v tem primeru se izbor "
"nikoli samodejno ne shrani v zgodovino odložišča. Glejte <xref linkend="
"\"clipboard-modes\"/>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid "Non-text selection"
msgstr "Nebesedilni izbor"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option determines whether non-text selections (such as images) are "
"saved in the clipboard history. It is possible to choose between "
"<guilabel>Always save in history</guilabel>, <guilabel>Only when explicitly "
"copied</guilabel>, and <guilabel>Never save in history</guilabel>. The "
"<guilabel>Always save in history</guilabel> option is not available if "
"selection/clipboard synchronisation is turned off &dash; in this case the "
"selection is never automatically saved in the clipboard history. See <xref "
"linkend=\"clipboard-modes\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost določa, ali se nebesedilni izbori (kot so slike) shranijo v "
"zgodovino odložišča. Izbirate lahko med <guilabel>Vedno shrani v zgodovino</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Samo pri iekspilictnem kopiranju</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Nikoli ne shrani v zgodovino</guilabel>. Možnost <guilabel>Vedno "
"shrani v zgodovino</guilabel> ni na voljo, če je sinhronizacija izbira/"
"odložišče izklopljena &dash; v tem primeru se izbor nikoli samodejno ne "
"shrani v zgodovino odložišča. Glejte <xref linkend=\"clipboard-modes\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid "Action Menu"
msgstr "Meni Dejanj"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show action popup menu"
msgstr "Prikaži pojavni meni dejanj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the time that a popup menu will remain for if you do nothing with it."
msgstr ""
"Določi, kako dolgo bo ostal pojavni menu, če z njim ne boste ničesar počeli."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replay actions on an item selected from history"
msgstr "Ponovi dejanje na elementu, izbranem iz zgodovine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this is switched on, selecting an item from the history causes &klipper; "
"to display the actions pop-up on that item, if appropriate."
msgstr ""
"Če je vklopljeno to, povzroči izbira elementa iz zgodovine, da &klipper; "
"prikaže pojavni menu dejanj na tem elementu, če seveda ustrezajo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove white space when executing actions"
msgstr "Odstranite prazen prostor med izvajanjem dejanj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If selected, any white space (spaces, tabs, &etc;) at the beginning and end "
"of the clipboard contents will be removed before passing the clipboard "
"contents to an application. This is useful, for example, if the clipboard "
"contains a &URL; with spaces which, if opened by a web browser, would cause "
"an error."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrana, bo prazen prostor (presledki, zavihki &etc;) na začetku in "
"koncu vsebine odložišča odstranjen, preden se vsebina odložišča posreduje "
"aplikaciji. To je na primer uporabno, če odložišče vsebuje &URL; s "
"presledki, ki bi, če bi jih odprl spletni brskalnik, povzročili napako."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid "Include MIME actions"
msgstr "Vključi MIME dejanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If selected, include applications that can accept its &MIME; type of a file "
"name or URL selected in the popup menu."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrano, vključi aplikacije, ki lahko sprejmejo &MIME; vrsto imena "
"datoteke ali URL-ja, izbranega v pojavnem meniju."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid "Actions Configuration"
msgstr "Nastavitve dejanj"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing Expressions/Actions"
msgstr "Urejevanje izrazov/dejanj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the <guilabel>Actions</guilabel> page, double-click the regular "
"expression or action that you want to edit or select it and press the "
"<guibutton>Edit Action</guibutton> button. A dialog will appear in which the "
"expression text can be edited as you wish."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku <guilabel>Dejanja</guilabel> kliknite na regularen izraz ali "
"dejanje, ki ga želite urediti. Pojavilo se bo majhno polje, v katerem lahko "
"po urejate besedilo, kakor želite."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding Expressions/Actions"
msgstr "Dodajanje izrazov/dejanj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click the <guibutton>Add Action...</guibutton> button to add a regular "
"expression for &klipper; to match. &klipper; uses &Qt;'s "
"<classname>QRegularExpression</classname>, which uses PCRE (Perl Compatible "
"Regular Expressions)."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb <guibutton>Dodaj dejanje ...</guibutton>, da dodate običajni "
"izraz za &klipper; za ujemanje. &klipper; uporablja &Qt; "
"<classname>QRegularExpression</classname>, ki uporablja PCRE (združljiv z "
"regularni izrazi za Perl)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add a description of the regular expression type (&eg; <quote>HTTP "
"URL</quote>) by <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> clicking in the "
"<guilabel>Description</guilabel> column."
msgstr ""
"Dodate lahko opis vrste regularnega izraza tipa(&npr; <quote>HTTP URL</"
"quote>), tako da <mousebutton>leva</mousebutton> kliknete v stolpcu "
"<guilabel>Opis</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can find detailed information about the use of "
"<classname>QRegularExpression</classname> regular expressions in <ulink url="
"\"https://doc.qt.io/qt-5/qregularexpression.html#details\">the Qt upstream "
"documentation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Podrobne informacije o uporabi najdete <classname>QRegularExpression</"
"classname> regularni izrazi v <ulink url=\"https://doc.qt.io/qt-5/"
"qregularexpression.html#details\">Qt dokumentacija</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Edit the regular expression as described above. To add a command to execute, "
"click <guimenuitem>Add Command</guimenuitem> and edit the command in an in-"
"place text editing box. Double-clicking on a command allows you to edit it."
msgstr ""
"Uredite regularni izraz, kot je opisano zgoraj. Če želite dodati ukaz za "
"izvedbo, kliknite <guimenuitem>Dodaj ukaz</guimenuitem> in uredite ukaz v "
"postavite polje za urejanje besedila. Z dvojnim klikom na ukaz ga lahko "
"uredite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that <token>%s</token> in the command line is replaced with the "
"clipboard contents, &eg; if your command definition is "
"<userinput><command>kwrite</command> <token>%s</token></userinput> and your "
"clipboard contents are <filename>/home/phil/textfile</filename>, the command "
"<userinput><command>kwrite</command> <filename>/home/phil/textfile</"
"filename></userinput> will be run. To include <token>%s</token> in the "
"command line, escape it with a backslash, as so: <userinput>\\%s</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da je <token>%s</token> v ukazni vrstici nadomeščen z vsebino "
"odložišča, &eg;. če je vaša definicija ukaza <userinput><command>kwrite</"
"command> <token>%s</token></userinput> in je vaša vsebina odložišča "
"<filename>/home/phil/textfile</filename>, bo zagnan ukaz "
"<userinput><command>kwrite</command> <filename>/home/phil/textfile</"
"filename></userinput>. Če želite vključiti <token>%s</token> vukazno "
"vrstico, ga umaknite s poševnico nazaj, tako: <userinput>\\%s</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Entries <userinput><token>%0</token></userinput> through <userinput><token>"
"%9</token></userinput> will be replaced by the corresponding captured texts "
"from the match pattern."
msgstr ""
"Vnosi <userinput><token>%0</token></userinput> do <userinput><token>%9</"
"token></userinput> bodo nadomeščeni z ustreznimi zajetimi besedili iz vzorca "
"ujemanja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcuts Options"
msgstr "Možnosti bližnjic"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The shortcuts page allows you to change the keyboard shortcuts which are "
"used to access &klipper; functions. You can change the shortcut to one of "
"three things:"
msgstr ""
"Stran z bližnjicami vam omogoča spreminjanje bližnjic na tipkovnici, ki se "
"uporabljajo za dostop do zmožnosti programa &klipper;. Bližnjico lahko "
"spremenite v eno od treh stvari:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid "None"
msgstr "Nič"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid "The selected action cannot be accessed directly from the keyboard"
msgstr "Izbrano dejanje ni dosegljivo neposredno s tipkovnice"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default"
msgstr "Privzeto"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The selected action uses &klipper;'s default key. These are the shortcuts "
"referred to in this manual."
msgstr ""
"Izbrano dejanje uporablja &klipper;jevo privzeto tipko. To so bližnjice, "
"omenjene v tem priročniku."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:380
#, no-c-format
msgid "Custom"
msgstr "Po meri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid "The selected action is assigned to the keys you choose."
msgstr "Izbrano dejanje je pripeto tipkam, ki jih izberete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To choose a custom key for the action you have selected, click on "
"<guilabel>Custom</guilabel> and then <guilabel>None</guilabel>. Now type the "
"desired key combination on your keyboard, as in any &kde; application."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrati tipko po meri za dejanje, ki ste ga izbrali, kliknite "
"<guilabel>Po meri</guilabel> in nato <guilabel>Brez</guilabel>. Zdaj vnesite "
"želeno kombinacijo tipk na vaši tipkovnici, kot v vseh &kde; aplikacijah."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you define a shortcut for <guilabel>Open Klipper at Mouse Position</"
"guilabel> pressing this shortcut will open the &klipper; popup menu at the "
"position of the mouse cursor, instead of their default position (in the "
"&plasma; Panel). Useful if you use the mouse more than the keyboard."
msgstr ""
"Če določite bližnjico za <guilabel>Odpri Klipper na položaju miške</"
"guilabel> se s pritiskom na to bližnjico odpre &klipper; pojavni meni na "
"položaju kazalca miške, namesto na privzetem položaju (v plošči &plasma;). "
"Uporabno, če uporabljate miško več kot tipkovnico."

